channel.name: Find Global Symbols
channel.description:
This shows a helpful 'lint' like utility to detect global symbols that exist in a given translator project.
See http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/find-global-symbols
Best practice is not to define global symbols since it makes larger amounts of code harder to maintain.

from_http.commit_comment: changed function in module to CheckForGlobals to be consistent with main() - otherwise it is BLOODY CONFUSING :-) added help, updated comments
